        "text_tV34Ah": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "category_1": "Crafted",
            "content_1": "<p>Crafted with premium durum wheat and slow-dried for the perfect texture, our pasta brings the taste of Italy straight to your kitchen.</p>",
            "category_2": "Artisan",
            "content_2": "<p>Made with generations of pasta-making expertise, our artisanal pasta is more than just food—it’s tradition, passion, and flavor combined.</p>",
            "category_3": "Love",
            "content_3": "<p>Great pasta doesn’t need much—just quality ingredients and a little love. Elevate your home cooking with pasta that’s as delicious as it is simple.</p>"
          }
        },
